{{Infobox power station | name = Perleberg Solar Park | name_official = | image = | image_size = | image_caption = | image_alt = | location_map = Germany | location_map_size = | location_map_caption = | coordinates = {{coord|53|04|21|N|11|49|30|E|type:landmark_region:DE|display=inline,title}} | coordinates_ref = | country = Germany | location = [[Perleberg]] | status = O | construction_began = April 2012 | commissioned = June 30, 2012 | decommissioned = | cost = | owner = Gehrlicher Solar | operator = | solar_type = PV | ps_units_operational = 144,144 | solar_site_area = {{convert|64|ha|acre|abbr=on}} | ps_electrical_capacity = 35 [[Megawatts|MW]]<sub>p</sub> | ps_electrical_cap_fac = | ps_annual_generation = 33 [[GWh]] | website = | extra = }}
The '''Perleberg Solar Park''' is a [[photovoltaic power station]], with an installed capacity of 35&nbsp;[[megawatt]]s (MW). It uses 144,144 solar panels manufactured by Chinese company [[Yingli]]. The panels are mounted at a fixed angle on posts that are driven into the ground, at a former military airport.<ref>[http://www.solarserver.com/solar-magazine/solar-news/current/2012/kw35/gehrlicher-solar-connects-35-mwp-pv-plant-on-former-military-airport-perleberg-germany-to-the-grid.html Gehrlicher Solar connects 35 MWp PV plant on former military airport Perleberg, Germany to the grid] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130222080854/http://www.solarserver.com/solar-magazine/solar-news/current/2012/kw35/gehrlicher-solar-connects-35-mwp-pv-plant-on-former-military-airport-perleberg-germany-to-the-grid.html |date=2013-02-22 }}</ref><ref>[http://www.gehrlicher.com/fileadmin/user_upload/Factsheet_Perleberg_A4_en.pdf Solar Power Plant Perleberg]</ref><ref>[http://www.gehrlicher.com/us/home/press/details/article/gehrlicher-solar-connects-35-mwp-solarpark-perleberg-to-the-grid/ Gehrlicher Solar Connects 35 MW Solarpark Perleberg to the Grid]</ref><ref>[http://www.sma.de/en/products/references/perleberg-solar-park.html Perleberg] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130222082256/http://www.sma.de/en/products/references/perleberg-solar-park.html |date=2013-02-22 }}</ref>
